{"tid":758082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打自從啲環保撚過份反智之後開始抗拒環保？","createTime":"2018-07-27T11:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T00:34:46.000Z","uid":92376,"like":95,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ece83ae5a64a2dd74693c2803146e5155ab5824d","tid":758082,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"之前爭取埋啲M記凍飲唔主動比膠搞到人好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後就係開始講緊想叫人走飲筒，再用啲洗極都會好多菌既鐵飲筒去代替<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就係因為呢啲人，本來我同好多朋友係對環保唔反感架，但依家覺得好憎，好似去做一啲反抗既行為，例如有平口膠袋一定攞，回收筒話擺報紙既我就掟啲紙包飲品同汽水罐落去，鋁罐果格先掟返報紙雜誌，有時嬲嬲地直頭唔關事既垃圾都掟埋入去，無架環保撚做呢啲野做多左，咪物極必反囉屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3981ac71b81a0169475e9f9e65e4d4550adb22fb","tid":758082,"uid":10692,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:10:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"717b5ab4c7f9615d843dff3e5ce839e12c9c84be","tid":758082,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3981ac71b81a0169475e9f9e65e4d4550adb22fb","tid":758082,"uid":10692,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:10:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:11:39.000Z","msg":"明架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\